sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (Browser)
    participant Route as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Edge
    participant UI as Streamlit UI<br/>8501/TCP HTTP
    participant API as Backend API<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Ollama as Ollama LLM<br/>11434/TCP HTTP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP Password
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant BentoML as BentoML llm-optimizer<br/>(in-process)
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MC as RHOAI Model Catalog<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,BentoML: Flow 1: Recommendation Workflow
        User->>Route: Open Planner UI
        Route->>UI: HTTPS→HTTP proxy (TLS edge termination)
        User->>UI: Describe deployment needs (natural language)
        UI->>API: POST /api/v1/extract<br/>HTTP/8000
        API->>Ollama: POST /api/chat<br/>HTTP/11434<br/>(intent extraction prompt)
        Ollama-->>API: Structured intent JSON
        API->>PG: SELECT benchmarks<br/>WHERE model/gpu/slo match<br/>5432/TCP Password auth
        PG-->>API: Benchmark results
        API->>HF: GET model config<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
        HF-->>API: Model architecture metadata
        alt No benchmark data available
            API->>BentoML: Roofline estimation<br/>(in-process Python call)
            BentoML-->>API: Estimated TTFT, ITL, throughput
        end
        API->>API: Score & rank configurations<br/>(accuracy, price, latency, complexity)
        API-->>UI: Ranked recommendations with YAML
        UI-->>User: Display 5 ranked views<br/>+ deployment specs
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over User,K8s: Flow 2: Kubernetes Deployment
        User->>UI: Click "Deploy to Cluster"
        UI->>API: POST /api/v1/deploy-to-cluster<br/>HTTP/8000
        API->>API: Jinja2 template rendering<br/>(InferenceService + HPA + ServiceMonitor)
        API->>K8s: kubectl apply -f<br/>HTTPS/6443 SA Token<br/>(subprocess call)
        K8s-->>API: Deployment result
        API-->>UI: Deployment status + YAML contents
        UI-->>User: Deployment confirmation
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over API,MC: Flow 3: Model Catalog Sync (Background)
        Note right of API: Triggered when<br/>PLANNER_BENCHMARK_SOURCE=model_catalog
        API->>MC: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/...<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS (service-serving CA)<br/>Bearer Token / SA Token
        MC-->>API: Model + artifact list
        API->>PG: UPSERT benchmark data<br/>5432/TCP Password auth
        API->>API: Refresh in-memory catalogs<br/>(ModelCatalog, UseCaseQualityScorer)
    end
